_the_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Jessica Springsteen, the daughter of musician legendBruce Springsteen, will not be competing in the 2024 Paris Olympics, just years after she represented the USA in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 590, \"end\": 609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Springsteen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Springsteen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Springsteen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Springsteen\"}, {\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9297489496797994, \"rank\": 0.07455981050409081, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9982360131989378, \"rank\": 0.0017669809157298741, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, Springsteen was competing forTeam USA's three-personequestrianjumping team.\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 808, \"end\": 811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9297489496797994, \"rank\": 0.07455981050409081, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kent Farrington, Laura Kraut, and McLain Ward made the cut and will represent the US at the Olympics inParislater this month, according to a July 6 announcement.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 850, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kent_Farrington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kent Farrington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kent_Farrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kent_Farrington\"}, {\"begin\": 867, \"end\": 878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kraut\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Kraut\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kraut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kraut\"}, {\"begin\": 884, \"end\": 895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McLain_Ward\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"McLain Ward\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McLain_Ward\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McLain_Ward\"}, {\"begin\": 932, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9912181854550087, \"rank\": 0.0078074227711807725, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Springsteen had been one of 10 athletes who made theshortlist for the Olympic squadin April.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1105, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As of Monday, Springsteen is ranked 89th in theGlobal Champions League standings.\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5815959540762935e-19, \"text\": \"Champions League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When she made the 2020 Olympics - which took place in 2021 because of the Covid-19 pandemic - she ranked 14th.\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Although she will not be competing in the Olympics this year, the 32-year-old has competed in the Olympics before.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was a member of the silver-medal-winning team that competed in Tokyo in 2021.\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9982360131989378, \"rank\": 0.0017669809157298741, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That same year, she was part of a team that took home the gold medal in the Mercedes-Benz Nations Cup at CHIO Aachen.\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mercedes-Benz\", \"score\": 0.9930114512501339, \"rank\": 0.0063759854241613005, \"text\": \"Mercedes-Benz\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mercedes-Benz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mercedes-Benz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More recently, the equestrian was part of the winning teams at the FEI Jumping Nations Cup of USA at San Juan Capistrano CSIO5 as well as the Global Champions Tour Grand Prix of London CSI5.\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1637, \"end\": 1647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9996186179240137, \"rank\": 0.0003772886151796875, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In May, she toldHarper's Bazaarthat she would have loved to bring her family - including her superstar father - to France.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1925, \"end\": 1931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7066894702451669, \"rank\": 0.29513290582744645, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tokyo 2020 was such an incredible experience, but because of that year and all the COVID-19 pandemic restrictions, you know, you could not have your family and your friends there,\\\" Springsteen told the magazine.\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 2146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2018, \"end\": 2035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.999980118188945, \"rank\": 1.560315664491811e-05, \"text\": \"COVID-19 pandemic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued: \\\"So I was like, 'Oh my gosh, I would love to go to another Olympics and be able to share that with my family,' who have been so supportive of my career for so many years.\\\"\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Years ago, her father had remarked on how proud he was of her career at aUS Equestrian Team Foundation fundraiser in 2016: \\\"Patti and my life has been deeply enriched by our involvement in the riding world.\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2408, \"end\": 2411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9839800075121533, \"rank\": 0.010405989899748764, \"text\": \"aUS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have gotten to watch my daughter grow up into a young woman of character and excellence.\\\"\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The musician continued: \\\"I have gotten to watch a lot of you grow up with her.\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have gotten to watch the best in the world compete year after year, and I know what that takes.\\\"\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 3045, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2866, \"end\": 2877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999992398898, \"rank\": 7.499043819041758e-10, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"